Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Episode 2: There's Something Every Hero\NNeeds at the Start of Their Journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, heroes!\NEpisode 2: There's Something Every Hero\NNeeds at the Start of Their Journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.55,0:00:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Lift your heads.\NEpisode 2: There's Something Every Hero\NNeeds at the Start of Their Journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard tell of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.06,0:00:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighter, the daughter of the\Nlegendary hero who saved my country!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.42,0:00:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy you've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.23,0:00:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm honored, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.35,0:00:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And Paladin, famous for her beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and her many victories!\NHow divine is your countenance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're far too kind, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And the genius who mastered the art\Nof magic at such a young age, Mage!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.03,0:00:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you would come, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.28,0:00:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my... you're embarrassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.36,0:00:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And Dark Elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.59,0:00:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They say you're wise,\Nand a deadly warrior as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So my reputation extends\Neven to the middle of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you four are here,\Neverything will be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.82,0:01:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I'd had your aid sooner,\Nthis never would've happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire world is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.04,0:01:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We four are here to save the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.28,0:01:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let them get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do our absolute best!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave everything to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad to hear it!\NI'm counting on you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.31,0:01:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?  What?  We're done talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.35,0:01:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to make some preparations\Nto fight the enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you some funds for your journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.93,0:01:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...\NOne, two, three, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm seeing right,\Nthere are ten gold pieces here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.35,0:01:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,King!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Nyou're telling us to save the world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,without enough money\Nto buy a single herb?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-that's rude!\NThere's no way he would possibly-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.  That's all you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!  A single night\Nat an inn costs 12 gold these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandpa gets a 100 gold\Npension every month...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then at least lend us the\Nlegendary weapon kept in this castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No!  There's no such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You just had a "Oh, that?" look on\Nyour face for a second, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're imagining it.  Now go, heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then first,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,sell some of the weapons of\Nthose stupid-looking soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,who do nothing but stand there all day,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and get us some money, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You would insult us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:03:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're insulting me much more,\Ntelling me to sell my body for just 10 gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nobody's saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I'm pretty sure if we don't fight,\Nthis country is doomed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is more important:\Nyour nation, or your money?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,King, make your choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The rope's rubbing me\Nsomeplace very personal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't look at me!